text.tspan: Protein production, grams per person per day
Total protein production from primary crop production, measured in average daily per capita terms (grams per
person per day). These values represent food production prior to global trade, and crop allocation for alternative
uses such as animal feed and industrial processes.
Source: Food system efficiency for grapher - Hannah Test
